{
  "stem": "12462.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead, someone recommended me for the Inspector General's Office, and I eventually rose through the-- several ranks of sergeant to warrant officer in the first few months in England.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we travelled all over England and Scotland and Northern Ireland investigating or in inspecting Army installations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had drew up a checklist, for which I was recommended for some damn honor, in order that people, when we left, could have a listing of the kinds of things that they should be watching out for.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we wouldn't give them to these until after we had inspected them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was considered to be quite an innovative idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I got taken to North Africa by the Assistant Inspector General in England, and Colonel Tom Brand then arranged for me to get a-- I got a direct commission in North Africa.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to go in at the bottom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went in as a second lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the-- the Allies invaded North Africa in late November, early December 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My language ability rested mainly on having had three and a half years of German at University of Wisconsin and North Central College.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I constantly reduced the amount of interest I had in the language, and my grades fell from A to C.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't really a very brilliant speaker in-- in German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could get along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I often had to be the interpreter in some way, particularly if the other person, the German, knew a little English between us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would get along pretty well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, what were your duties in North Africa?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I became the administrative officer to the Inspector General of the Mediterranean Base Section.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
